
 This directory contains utilities for the TextMine package.

 Files 			Description
 ------------		---------------------------------------------------
 compile.pl		Compile perl scripts in directories
 configure.pl		Script to configure Constants.pm
 db_proc.pl		Script to backup/restore tables
 em_b_delete.pl		Delete the e-mails marked for deletion
 em_b_receive.pl	Read a file and load the e-mails into the table
 fetch_b_url.pl		Fetch the URL in batch
 install.pl		Script to copy files to web directories
 load_mod.pl		Load the dependent Perl modules
 load_tab.pl		Load the DB tables
 me_b_index.pl		Index files in directories
 me_b_repair.pl		Fix an index that is not in sync with file names
 ne_collector.pl	Collect, index, summarize, and cluster news articles
 pack.pl		Compress read only DB tables
 run_collector.pl	Script to run the news collector in parallel
 run_fetch		Script to fetch an URL
 setup.pl		Create and load the database
 sp_log.pl		Script to dump the log for a particular crawl
 sp_b_spider.pl		Spider script to crawl the web
 tables.sql		SQL to load tables

 Directories		Description
 ------------		--------------------------------------------------
 data			Files to load DB tables
